cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

This paper deals with natural language processing and reinforcement learning to solve text-based games. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper proposes a new approach to generate valid commands, which involves training a model, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category. The paper also involves human-computer interaction, which makes cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves generating data using Textworld, which makes cs.SD (Software Engineering) another possible category.
